article.description: — Francis Nwaokorie had 19 points off the bench to carry UC San Diego to a 75-55 win over George Washington on Saturday night.
article.headline: Nwaokorie leads UC San Diego past George Washington 75-55
article.linkText: Nwaokorie leads UC San Diego past George Washington 75-55
article.story: SAN DIEGO -- — Francis Nwaokorie had 19 points off the bench to carry UC San Diego to a 75-55 win over George Washington on Saturday night. Jake Kosakowski had 12 points for UC San Diego (2-0). Jace Roquemore added 11 points. Toni Rocak had 11 points and seven rebounds. Ricky Lindo Jr. had 13 points and 11 rebounds for the Colonials (1-2). Brendan Adams added 12 points.
